snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer - Kannada | Rishab Shetty | Rukmini | Vijay Kiragandur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films — the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar — and the visionary, National Award–winning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend – Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend – Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations.

snippet.title: PHÙ ĐỔNG THIÊN VƯƠNG - ĐỨC PHÚC | 🇻🇳 VIỆT NAM | WINNER OF THE INTERVISION 2025
snippet.description:
#DucPhuc #phudongthienvuong #intervision2025 #ducphucintervision #vietnam

PHÙ ĐỔNG THIÊN VƯƠNG 🎍 - ĐỨC PHÚC | VIỆT NAM | INTERVISION 2025 🏆

Là ca khúc được viết mới dành riêng cho chương trình Intervision 2025 mà Phúc cùng Team Việt Nam 🇻🇳 lựa chọn.

Nhạc Sĩ: HỒ HOÀI ANH
Hoà Âm, Phối Khí: DƯƠNG K
Cảm Hứng:
Bài thơ "Tre Việt Nam" của nhà thơ NGUYỄN DUY
Lời Bài Hát:
HỒ HOÀI ANH
PHÚC DU (Lời Rap)
ORANGE (Lời Tiếng Anh)

Tre xanh,
Xanh tự bao giờ?
Chuyện ngày xưa... đã có bờ tre xanh.

Mà sao nên luỹ nên thành tre ơi?

snippet.description:
Hey Raider, ready to head back Topside? 

Join the ARC Raiders Server Slam! Doors open from October 17th - 19th. No codes, everyone is invited! Jump in, battle for loot, and push the servers to their limits in this expansive Extraction Adventure from Embark Studios. 

ARC Raiders is available for pre-order now: https://arcraiders.com/#purchase 
___
Follow for the latest news: 
X:  https://twitter.com/ARCRaidersGame
Discord:  https://discord.gg/arcraiders
___
SCAVENGE, SURVIVE, THRIVE
In ARC Raiders, gameplay flows between the dangerous surface and the underground stronghold of Speranza. Progress your character and build up your workshop so you can craft, prep, and upgrade before venturing Topside to scavenge and explore. Encounter the constant threat of machine and the unpredictable choices of fellow survivors. Go solo or in parties up to three. In the end, only you decide what kind of Raider you are and how far you’ll go to endure.
